 Ultra magnus opened his compartment. The room shined with light as the 
matrix layed with him. "It was given to me, for safe keeping. Rodimus can not 
know of it yet. For if there is  a chance our forces get control back of 
Prime he'll arrive here searching for the matrix to win the war. The Elders 
felt I was the only one left trust worthy. There has been a lot of maximals 
turning on us...if you can believe it. It is best to wait and see. What is 
this you say about Galvatron?" the matrix slowly went back into the 
compartment in his chest.

--part1_26.2f7835f4.2adf5050_boundary
